OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mainly dry
OL,6,Fand bright evening with some late hazy
OL,7,Fsunshine. The rest of the night will
OL,8,Fremain dry for most, but the odd
OL,9,Fshower possible in the west later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FA dry and bright start to the
OL,12,Fday with patchy cloud. Showers will
OL,13,Fdevelop for the afternoon, some of
OL,14,Fwhich may be heavy and thundery.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,17,Fand settled throughout this period.
OL,18,FThere'll be plenty of good sunny
OL,19,Fspells inland, especially during
OL,20,Fafternoons, however areas of cloud
OL,21,Fwill often affect eastern coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
